Title: Not in Chee-Chee's Backyard
Description:
Not all hozen are the same. Chee-Chee's tribe was forest hozen... came from Jade Forest. Pretty easy to get along with.

The Kunzen invaders... they come from mountains, far to the north. Not nearly as nice as Chee-Chee.

They come into our green land, take our things, leave big mess behind.

Chee-Chee wants to kill them. You like to help?
ObjectivesText: Kill 8 members of the Kunzen tribe in the Kunzen Village.
